sentences.english: Objective To evaluate the anatomy and HRCT findings of foramen of nasal bone.

sentences.english: It is proved that DR imaging is an ideal method of nasal bone examination.

sentences.english: The consonants at the end of the English words sun , sum , and sung are nasals .
